WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.230
Hey, good morning family. Praise the

00:00:02.240 --> 00:00:04.390
Lord. Thank you for joining me today.

00:00:04.400 --> 00:00:08.470
Well, we see that Canada has

00:00:08.470 --> 00:00:08.480
chosen

00:00:08.480 --> 00:00:12.709
their leader. I saw

00:00:12.719 --> 00:00:15.829
this coming several weeks ago, but I did

00:00:15.839 --> 00:00:19.310
not want to come out and try to

00:00:19.320 --> 00:00:22.630
discourage the believers

00:00:22.640 --> 00:00:24.470
there. I was like,

00:00:24.480 --> 00:00:25.910
'Let's stand in faith that we can

00:00:25.920 --> 00:00:28.230
turn this thing.'And when I was in

00:00:28.240 --> 00:00:30.070
prayer yesterday with you all in that

00:00:30.080 --> 00:00:32.310
video, I saw the people crying. I saw

00:00:32.320 --> 00:00:35.030
Canadians crying because of the way the

00:00:35.040 --> 00:00:37.590
election went. They were weeping. I saw

00:00:37.600 --> 00:00:40.470
women crying. I saw people upset because

00:00:40.480 --> 00:00:43.030
of the turnout—believers that were

00:00:43.040 --> 00:00:44.950
upset about how their

00:00:44.960 --> 00:00:47.830
nation was going. And so if you go back

00:00:47.840 --> 00:00:49.270
and watch that, that's what I was

00:00:49.280 --> 00:00:52.750
seeing. I saw an

00:00:52.760 --> 00:00:55.830
uprising. People were upset about the

00:00:55.840 --> 00:00:57.670
turnout. Some people were

00:00:57.680 --> 00:00:59.189
saying, 'Hey, we're going to

00:00:59.199 --> 00:01:01.110
stand for what we want to stand

00:01:01.110 --> 00:01:01.120
for.'And

00:01:01.120 --> 00:01:04.229
there was an uprising in

00:01:04.239 --> 00:01:05.990
the Christian community in the

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:08.710
days ahead because of the liberal

00:01:08.720 --> 00:01:10.550
beliefs and the liberal way they were

00:01:10.560 --> 00:01:12.270
wanting to take your

00:01:12.280 --> 00:01:16.149
nation. I saw the same thing

00:01:16.159 --> 00:01:18.950
going on in Australia. But there were

00:01:18.960 --> 00:01:21.910
little fires; they weren't big fires. I

00:01:21.920 --> 00:01:24.870
saw little fires in Queensland,

00:01:24.880 --> 00:01:26.149
Australia.

00:01:26.159 --> 00:01:28.149
I don't

00:01:28.159 --> 00:01:29.510
know what that was all about,

00:01:29.520 --> 00:01:31.030
but people were upset and they were

00:01:31.040 --> 00:01:33.030
rising up. They were rising up against

00:01:33.040 --> 00:01:34.310
the government

00:01:34.310 --> 00:01:34.320
and

00:01:34.320 --> 00:01:36.310
the decisions that were being

00:01:36.320 --> 00:01:38.390
made because they didn't like the way it

00:01:38.400 --> 00:01:41.990
was turning. As we see this, I told

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:44.310
you I saw the barrels, those whiskey

00:01:44.320 --> 00:01:47.429
barrels rolling down from Canada into

00:01:47.439 --> 00:01:50.870
America because of the trade. I saw

00:01:50.880 --> 00:01:53.590
a global depression

00:01:53.600 --> 00:01:55.830
hitting the economy of Canada in the

00:01:55.840 --> 00:01:58.789
days ahead, similar to America. But then

00:01:58.799 --> 00:02:02.550
I saw that British

00:02:02.550 --> 00:02:02.560
Columbia

00:02:02.560 --> 00:02:05.109
wanted to stand out on their own because

00:02:05.119 --> 00:02:06.950
they wanted to be a part of the

00:02:06.960 --> 00:02:09.190
digital platform and all the

00:02:09.200 --> 00:02:11.110
things that are going on. I don't know

00:02:11.120 --> 00:02:13.589
if that's later on, but I saw

00:02:13.599 --> 00:02:15.830
this, so I don't know the timing of it.

00:02:15.840 --> 00:02:17.589
I'm just piecing together

00:02:17.599 --> 00:02:19.830
what I've gotten in prayer, bringing

00:02:19.840 --> 00:02:21.270
it out to you to give you hope that

00:02:21.280 --> 00:02:24.150
there will be a revival in Canada. It

00:02:24.160 --> 00:02:26.190
will come out of a great

00:02:26.200 --> 00:02:28.630
pressure, but there will be a major

00:02:28.640 --> 00:02:30.949
revival in the days ahead. I'm

00:02:30.959 --> 00:02:32.470
telling you all, the best is yet to come

00:02:32.480 --> 00:02:34.790
for the body of Christ concerning the

00:02:34.800 --> 00:02:37.430
harvest of the souls. So now what we do

00:02:37.440 --> 00:02:40.030
is pray for your

00:02:40.040 --> 00:02:43.750
leaders. Like I said, it was because

00:02:43.760 --> 00:02:46.390
of the body of Christ—the preachers not

00:02:46.400 --> 00:02:49.589
having a backbone in Canada and not

00:02:49.599 --> 00:02:52.070
preaching an uncompromising word—is what

00:02:52.080 --> 00:02:53.670
I was seeing. Remember I told you all I

00:02:53.680 --> 00:02:55.190
went in the spirit and I was praying

00:02:55.200 --> 00:02:57.430
with you a couple of weeks ago and I saw

00:02:57.440 --> 00:03:00.630
the preachers. I saw a lukewarmness

00:03:00.640 --> 00:03:02.949
in the churches, and the Lord said

00:03:02.959 --> 00:03:04.869
because of this

00:03:04.879 --> 00:03:06.710
lukewarmness, we're praying and we're

00:03:06.720 --> 00:03:08.710
upset about the politics, but the problem

00:03:08.720 --> 00:03:10.949
is we're not preaching the gospel in the

00:03:10.959 --> 00:03:12.710
churches that causes the culture to

00:03:12.720 --> 00:03:15.750
change. Because as the church goes, so

00:03:15.760 --> 00:03:18.390
does everything else. As the preachers

00:03:18.400 --> 00:03:19.990
don't stand on the word, so does

00:03:20.000 --> 00:03:21.309
everything

00:03:21.319 --> 00:03:23.910
else. The Lord warned me and even told

00:03:23.920 --> 00:03:26.390
me this is a wake-up call. We

00:03:26.400 --> 00:03:28.229
have a reprieve in America,

00:03:28.239 --> 00:03:30.789
a four-year window of Trump, and he even

00:03:30.799 --> 00:03:31.630
told

00:03:31.640 --> 00:03:35.110
me, 'We're wanting everything to be on

00:03:35.120 --> 00:03:38.869
Trump's shoulders to fix

00:03:38.869 --> 00:03:38.879
America.'Well,

00:03:38.879 --> 00:03:40.710
it's on America; it's on him

00:03:40.720 --> 00:03:42.949
now. But the bottom line was when I

00:03:42.959 --> 00:03:47.110
saw the sticky substance,

00:03:47.120 --> 00:03:49.830
this oily honey coming off the

00:03:49.830 --> 00:03:49.840
preachers'mouths,

00:03:49.840 --> 00:03:51.750
and cockroaches were

00:03:51.760 --> 00:03:53.589
coming in and out of the mouths and

00:03:53.599 --> 00:03:55.509
laying upon the lips of the preachers in

00:03:55.519 --> 00:03:58.309
America. I saw babies across the

00:03:58.319 --> 00:04:00.630
land with diapers on. And the Lord

00:04:00.640 --> 00:04:02.869
warned me. He said, 'The preachers are

00:04:02.879 --> 00:04:05.190
not preaching the meat of the word.

00:04:05.200 --> 00:04:08.229
They're preaching a milk gospel to

00:04:08.239 --> 00:04:10.470
the people.'And this is what's wrong

00:04:10.480 --> 00:04:13.429
with America, because the preachers are

00:04:13.439 --> 00:04:15.990
not preaching an uncompromising word

00:04:16.000 --> 00:04:18.069
that teaches people how to live by faith

00:04:18.079 --> 00:04:20.469
and to grow up strong—the ABCs of

00:04:20.479 --> 00:04:23.909
faith.

00:04:23.919 --> 00:04:26.070
So the babies were all across the

00:04:26.080 --> 00:04:27.830
land, but it wasn't just America; it was

00:04:27.840 --> 00:04:30.310
going across the whole world.

00:04:30.320 --> 00:04:33.430
This is a global problem where people

00:04:33.440 --> 00:04:35.430
need to wake up and preach the gospel

00:04:35.440 --> 00:04:37.270
the way it needs to be preached and not

00:04:37.280 --> 00:04:40.390
this compromising, lukewarm gospel.

00:04:40.400 --> 00:04:42.230
The Lord warned me this was

00:04:42.240 --> 00:04:44.550
coming and that people needed to have a

00:04:44.560 --> 00:04:46.189
backbone like a

00:04:46.199 --> 00:04:49.270
crowbar

00:04:49.280 --> 00:04:51.590
because what is coming is going to

00:04:51.600 --> 00:04:53.070
shake the

00:04:53.080 --> 00:04:56.790
world. We see fruit of it now. We pray

00:04:56.800 --> 00:05:00.670
for South Korea because I saw a

00:05:00.680 --> 00:05:04.310
communist party trying to rise up in

00:05:04.310 --> 00:05:04.320
Korea—as

00:05:04.320 --> 00:05:08.790
bad as

00:05:08.800 --> 00:05:11.510
North Korea—that it would try to be

00:05:11.520 --> 00:05:13.670
a little

00:05:13.680 --> 00:05:15.749
bit, a little bit, and it equals a lot. Do

00:05:15.759 --> 00:05:16.950
you see what I'm saying? It wasn't just

00:05:16.960 --> 00:05:19.749
all at once; it was like a frog in a pot

00:05:19.759 --> 00:05:21.830
being

00:05:21.840 --> 00:05:24.150
boiled and cooked alive and it

00:05:24.160 --> 00:05:25.430
didn't even know as the temperature

00:05:25.440 --> 00:05:28.710
rises. As the

00:05:28.720 --> 00:05:30.870
South Koreans adapted to it, the

00:05:30.880 --> 00:05:33.270
communistic party of China was

00:05:33.280 --> 00:05:36.150
influencing North Korea, and North Korea

00:05:36.160 --> 00:05:38.310
had its hand trying to influence and

00:05:38.320 --> 00:05:40.310
take

00:05:40.320 --> 00:05:42.550
down South Korea and

00:05:42.560 --> 00:05:45.749
Taiwan. As we see, they were

00:05:45.759 --> 00:05:47.990
trying to bring them in like a mother

00:05:48.000 --> 00:05:50.390
hen tries to bring in her

00:05:50.390 --> 00:05:50.400
chicks.

00:05:50.400 --> 00:05:52.469
That's what China was doing—trying to

00:05:52.479 --> 00:05:55.270
bring in those islands that they

00:05:55.280 --> 00:05:57.270
looked at as rebellious. 'You're not

00:05:57.280 --> 00:05:58.990
underneath

00:05:59.000 --> 00:06:01.270
communism, and we need to bring you into

00:06:01.280 --> 00:06:04.150
the way we think.'It's a demonic way

00:06:04.160 --> 00:06:05.909
of thinking; it's bondage. And there's

00:06:05.919 --> 00:06:07.990
an iron curtain there that keeps

00:06:08.000 --> 00:06:10.710
Christianity out. The people of

00:06:10.720 --> 00:06:13.029
South Korea have become complacent,

00:06:13.039 --> 00:06:15.350
and so it was with so many other places

00:06:15.350 --> 00:06:15.360
where

00:06:15.360 --> 00:06:16.790
they don't want to lose their

00:06:16.800 --> 00:06:19.029
freedom. And the Lord told me,

00:06:19.039 --> 00:06:21.029
'This is what's going to happen if the

00:06:21.039 --> 00:06:22.870
people don't rise up and take their

00:06:22.880 --> 00:06:25.830
authority, humble themselves

00:06:25.840 --> 00:06:27.430
and pray, and turn from their wicked

00:06:27.440 --> 00:06:29.510
ways, then they will hear from

00:06:29.520 --> 00:06:31.110
heaven and the Lord said he would heal

00:06:31.120 --> 00:06:33.430
your land.'I'm telling you all, it's a

00:06:33.440 --> 00:06:36.550
time like never before to be serious,

00:06:36.560 --> 00:06:39.749
looking at the

00:06:39.759 --> 00:06:41.350
signs of the times. So

00:06:41.360 --> 00:06:43.830
what do we do now? Canada's gone

00:06:43.840 --> 00:06:45.870
left again. We pray for

00:06:45.880 --> 00:06:48.230
revival. We pray

00:06:48.240 --> 00:06:50.629
that Australia goes

00:06:50.639 --> 00:06:52.390
better. We pray for South Korea.

00:06:52.400 --> 00:06:54.029
They're coming up really

00:06:54.039 --> 00:06:57.270
quick. And so, we pray for America.

00:06:57.280 --> 00:06:59.909
We pray for our economic situation.

00:06:59.919 --> 00:07:01.909
People say, 'Brandon, you know, in that

00:07:01.919 --> 00:07:03.189
video yesterday, there were so many

00:07:03.199 --> 00:07:05.670
people that agreed about

00:07:05.680 --> 00:07:07.110
number three.'I told you to pick one,

00:07:07.120 --> 00:07:09.430
two, or three. There were a lot of people

00:07:09.440 --> 00:07:11.909
that agreed with three—that we have a

00:07:11.919 --> 00:07:15.350
window, but the window is based on who

00:07:15.360 --> 00:07:18.309
will pray. Who will pray for this wealth

00:07:18.319 --> 00:07:21.510
transfer? It's not going to just happen.

00:07:21.520 --> 00:07:24.390
You see the wrecking

00:07:24.400 --> 00:07:28.150
ball swinging and we must pray for a

00:07:28.160 --> 00:07:30.070
window of opportunity. God said, 'I want

00:07:30.080 --> 00:07:31.589
to give you a window.'But what is that

00:07:31.599 --> 00:07:33.589
based on? People interceding just

00:07:33.599 --> 00:07:36.629
like Abraham—people interceding and

00:07:36.639 --> 00:07:38.790
praying for the

00:07:38.800 --> 00:07:41.029
window. As

00:07:41.029 --> 00:07:41.039
the watchman

00:07:41.039 --> 00:07:42.710
on

00:07:42.720 --> 00:07:44.710
the wall, I am warning you of

00:07:44.720 --> 00:07:47.510
what's coming: shortages of food

00:07:47.510 --> 00:07:47.520
and

00:07:47.520 --> 00:07:51.670
goods. Well, 'we

00:07:51.680 --> 00:07:53.350
don't need China's

00:07:53.350 --> 00:07:53.360
stuff.'Folks,

00:07:53.360 --> 00:07:56.070
it's bigger than that. It's

00:07:57.360 --> 00:07:59.909
car parts. I saw

00:07:59.919 --> 00:08:01.909
people not being able to fix

00:08:01.919 --> 00:08:05.029
their cars, chips for the cars, things

00:08:05.039 --> 00:08:08.309
that were very tied to computers

00:08:08.309 --> 00:08:08.319
and

00:08:08.319 --> 00:08:12.950
our electric grid. I saw major

00:08:12.960 --> 00:08:16.230
power outages coming. Have I not

00:08:16.240 --> 00:08:18.150
warned you of this? Clear back in the

00:08:18.160 --> 00:08:21.350
summer of last year, I said I've seen

00:08:21.360 --> 00:08:24.950
major cyber attacks coming from China.

00:08:24.960 --> 00:08:27.110
I warned you

00:08:27.120 --> 00:08:29.990
back in July. I saw

00:08:30.000 --> 00:08:32.149
people without electricity in some

00:08:32.159 --> 00:08:34.909
cities for three

00:08:34.919 --> 00:08:38.070
weeks because of some kind

00:08:38.080 --> 00:08:40.630
of hack or computer problems.

00:08:40.640 --> 00:08:42.630
It was so bad that it caused the

00:08:42.640 --> 00:08:45.269
whole infrastructure to melt down,

00:08:45.279 --> 00:08:47.990
mainly on the East Coast.

00:08:48.000 --> 00:08:50.230
I've warned you of this. So why do you

00:08:50.240 --> 00:08:51.750
bring all that up, Brandon? Because Italy

00:08:51.750 --> 00:08:51.760
is

00:08:51.760 --> 00:08:54.230
having issues. I don't know what

00:08:54.240 --> 00:08:56.070
caused all those issues, but a lot of

00:08:56.080 --> 00:08:57.910
power outages happened in France and

00:08:57.920 --> 00:09:00.230
Italy today. And those people had to

00:09:00.240 --> 00:09:01.910
walk out of subways. They had to walk;

00:09:01.920 --> 00:09:03.269
they didn't have power, they didn't have

00:09:03.279 --> 00:09:04.630
cell phones, they didn't have anything.

00:09:04.640 --> 00:09:06.389
I said it seemed like an

00:09:06.389 --> 00:09:06.399
EMP—that's

00:09:06.399 --> 00:09:07.670
what it seemed like. Like

00:09:07.680 --> 00:09:10.150
something major went on and they had

00:09:10.160 --> 00:09:12.949
a major grid meltdown. So then

00:09:12.959 --> 00:09:16.550
I hear that Russia and North Korea

00:09:16.560 --> 00:09:18.070
are being buddies and they're trying to

00:09:18.080 --> 00:09:21.030
raise up even more.

00:09:21.040 --> 00:09:25.829
I told you: watch North Korea and Russia

00:09:25.839 --> 00:09:28.750
in the days ahead. I have seen these two

00:09:28.760 --> 00:09:32.630
countries in meetings—major meetings

00:09:32.640 --> 00:09:35.350
about bringing troops over, bringing

00:09:35.360 --> 00:09:37.949
them out of the Western

00:09:37.949 --> 00:09:37.959
bloc

00:09:37.959 --> 00:09:41.829
because America has suppressed

00:09:41.829 --> 00:09:41.839
them—North

00:09:41.839 --> 00:09:43.670
Korea because of communism

00:09:43.680 --> 00:09:45.269
and all the things that are going on

00:09:45.269 --> 00:09:45.279
with

00:09:45.279 --> 00:09:46.949
how they treat their people. Well,

00:09:46.959 --> 00:09:49.350
Russia was saying, "Hey, you join up

00:09:49.360 --> 00:09:50.670
with

00:09:50.680 --> 00:09:53.630
us and we will bring you into the BRICS. We'll bring you into the

00:09:53.640 --> 00:09:55.509
BRICS."So

00:09:55.519 --> 00:09:58.070
what we're seeing right

00:09:58.080 --> 00:10:01.670
now, I saw in visions. I

00:10:01.680 --> 00:10:03.190
haven't made a lot of this public. I saw

00:10:03.200 --> 00:10:06.310
them laughing at Trump.

00:10:06.320 --> 00:10:09.030
They were making fun of

00:10:09.040 --> 00:10:11.110
him, thinking, "This old man is trying to

00:10:11.120 --> 00:10:13.910
control us. You are not going to control

00:10:13.910 --> 00:10:13.920
us."And

00:10:13.920 --> 00:10:15.910
the way they were acting

00:10:15.920 --> 00:10:19.030
was, "We're not going to allow you to

00:10:19.040 --> 00:10:21.829
try to dominate us."And they were trying

00:10:21.839 --> 00:10:23.590
to make alliances with Cuba and

00:10:23.600 --> 00:10:25.750
Venezuela and all these other countries

00:10:25.760 --> 00:10:28.470
in the days ahead. So we see these

00:10:28.480 --> 00:10:30.630
things coming to pass. And like

00:10:30.640 --> 00:10:33.110
I said, I told you I'm praying for

00:10:33.120 --> 00:10:35.350
the window—the window

00:10:35.360 --> 00:10:37.430
of where we are and that we're not going

00:10:37.440 --> 00:10:40.150
to have all this happen so

00:10:40.160 --> 00:10:42.630
quickly. But folks, we're pushing.

00:10:42.640 --> 00:10:44.550
It's like a

00:10:44.550 --> 00:10:44.560
teeter-totter.

00:10:44.560 --> 00:10:47.030
We're pushing things back in the spirit.

00:10:47.040 --> 00:10:50.310
We're holding things in balance because the

00:10:50.320 --> 00:10:53.670
adversary is wanting their time now. And

00:10:53.680 --> 00:10:56.150
remember what I told you. Jesus stood up

00:10:56.160 --> 00:10:58.870
and I saw him above the United

00:10:58.880 --> 00:11:01.110
States of America. And he said, "Who

00:11:01.120 --> 00:11:04.550
will stand in the gap for America? Who

00:11:04.560 --> 00:11:07.269
will pray for

00:11:07.269 --> 00:11:07.279
America?"If

00:11:07.279 --> 00:11:09.350
you remember what I told you all,

00:11:09.360 --> 00:11:11.750
Jesus said all that and I saw a

00:11:11.760 --> 00:11:14.150
massive python coming up out of the Gulf

00:11:14.160 --> 00:11:16.870
of Mexico, and it tried to wrap around

00:11:16.880 --> 00:11:19.949
America and squeeze it from the middle,

00:11:19.959 --> 00:11:22.630
trying to squeeze it from within. It

00:11:22.640 --> 00:11:24.949
was a massive python, a massive snake

00:11:24.949 --> 00:11:24.959
coming

00:11:24.959 --> 00:11:26.710
up out of the Gulf. And I saw a

00:11:26.720 --> 00:11:29.350
storm of communism, a storm of war, a

00:11:29.360 --> 00:11:32.470
storm of an Antichrist spirit

00:11:32.480 --> 00:11:34.870
trying to come over and trying to come

00:11:34.880 --> 00:11:37.230
on too fast. And the Lord wanted more

00:11:37.240 --> 00:11:39.590
time. And you say, "Well, can the Lord

00:11:39.600 --> 00:11:41.350
just have more time?"It comes through

00:11:41.360 --> 00:11:43.389
